{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"init","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"lightness","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt16","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s6UInt16V"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"hue","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt16","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s6UInt16V"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"saturation","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt16","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s6UInt16V"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The target value of the Light HSL Lightness state.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"lightness"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The target value of the Light HSL Hue state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"hue"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The target value of the Light HSL Saturation state.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"saturation"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The values for the Lightness state are defined in the following table:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0x0000 - light is not emitted by the element.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0x0001 - 0xFFFE - the perceived lightness of a light emitted by the element.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0xFFFF - the highest perceived lightness of a light emitted by the element.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Hue is representing by 16-bit unsigned integer of a 0-360 degree scale","